data.text:
The Zootopia Defence Force, also known as The Zootopian Armed Forces or just simply called the ZDF are the main military force that defends Zootopia, Bunnyburrow and to uphold the law and order along side the Zootopia Police Department (ZPD). The ZDF are also Zootopia's Military Police, Coast Guard, Navy, Air Force and they use top of the line military grade weapons, vehicles and technology but also both male and female can serve in in the ZDF just like in the ZPD.
